ZH: 我给你提醒，明天是你的生日。
EN: Let me remind you, tomorrow is your birthday.

ZH: 他提醒我参加会议的时间。
EN: He reminded me of the meeting time.

ZH: 请你提醒我明天去买火腿。
EN: Can you remind me to buy ham tomorrow?

ZH: 这个闹钟每天早上6点会提醒我起床。
EN: This alarm clock reminds me to wake up at 6 am every day.

ZH: 妈妈提醒我们要锁好门窗。
EN: Mom reminded us to lock the doors and windows.

ZH: 他经常提醒我注意时间，以免迟到。
EN: He frequently reminds me to be mindful of the time to avoid being late.

ZH: 我需要提醒你按时吃药。
EN: I need to remind you to take your medicine on time.

ZH: 请提醒我明天早上打电话给John。
EN: Please remind me to call John tomorrow morning.

ZH: 下雨了，别忘了提醒他带伞。
EN: It's raining, don't forget to remind him to bring an umbrella.

ZH: 在出门之前，我一定要提醒自己检查行李。
EN: Before leaving, I always remind myself to check my luggage.

ZH: 他提醒我及时还书。
EN: He reminded me to return the book in time.

ZH: 麻烦你提醒我交报告！
EN: Can you remind me to submit the report?

ZH: 我提醒你，明天有个重要的面试。
EN: I remind you that there is an important interview tomorrow.

ZH: 公共场所请提醒他人保持安静。
EN: Please remind others to keep quiet in public places.

ZH: 我自己不需要提醒，我已经记住了。
EN: I don't need a reminder, I already remembered it.

ZH: 他提醒我不要忘记交房租。
EN: He reminded me not to forget to pay the rent.

ZH: 上课的时候老师总是提醒我们注意听讲。
EN: The teacher always reminds us to pay attention in class.

ZH: 这个软件会定时提醒你喝水。
EN: This app will remind you to drink water regularly.

ZH: 当我感到紧张时，我需要提醒自己深呼吸。
EN: When I feel nervous, I need to remind myself to take deep breaths.

ZH: 提醒一下，明天有个重要的会议。
EN: Just a reminder, there is an important meeting tomorrow.
